title: Back Street [1961] DVD-rip
description:
Back Street (1961)
DVD-rip

Starring Susan Hayward, John Gavin, Vera Miles

"Back Street is a 1961 film made by Universal Pictures, directed by David Miller, and produced by Ross Hunter. The screenplay was written by William Ludwig and Eleanore Griffin based on novel by Fannie Hurst. The music score is by Frank Skinner."

This is one of the premier tear-jerker romances of the late 50's-early 60's. It "follows the long, unrequited romance between two people [Susan Hayward, John Gavin] over the years as they can't seem to ever get together the way they want to."

Nominated for Academy Award for Best Costume Design, Color (Jean Louis).

It must be noted this movie is not readily available at the usual DVD counters.

This file superseeds the unseeded previous upload.
